        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          Business Analyst<br><br>Strategy and Architecture <br>•	Technical Strategy and Planning <br>o	Methods and Tools (METL) – Level 2<br><br>Change and Transformation <br>•	Business Change Management <br>o	Business Analysis (BUAN) – Level 3<br>o	Business Modelling (BSMO) – Level 2<br>o	Requirements Definition and Management (REQM) – Level 3<br><br>Development and Implementation <br>•	User Experience <br>o	User Experience Analysis (UNAN) – Level 2<br><br>Relationships and Engagement <br>•	Stakeholder Management <br>o	Relationships Management (RLMT) – Level 2
