          Senior Technology Delivery Manager<br><br>Strategy and Architecture<br>•	Business Strategy and Planning<br>o	Financial and Commercial Management – level 3<br>o	Continuous Improvement – level 4<br>o	Business Risk Management (BURM) – level 4<br><br>Change and Transformation<br>•	Business Change Implementation<br>o	Project Management (PRMG) – level 4<br><br>Skills and Quality<br>•	Quality and Conformance<br>o	Quality Management (QUMG) – level 3<br><br>Relationships and Engagement<br>•	Stakeholder Management<br>o	Relationship Management (RLMT) – level 4
        </dd>
        
